@TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Get All Time Entries
GET {{TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress}}/api/timeentry
Accept: application/json

### Create FTE Time Entry (Regular Hours)
POST {{TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress}}/api/timeentry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "employeeName": "John Doe",
  "employeeType": "FTE",
  "startTime": "2024-11-27T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2024-11-27T17:00:00",
  "hourlyRate": 50.00,
  "notes": "Regular 8-hour shift",
  "yearsOfService": 3
}

