### Update Time Entry (Change ID to match created entry)
PUT {{TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress}}/api/timeentry/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "employeeName": "John Doe",
  "employeeType": "FTE",
  "startTime": "2024-11-27T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2024-11-27T18:00:00",
  "hourlyRate": 50.00,
  "notes": "Extended to 9 hours",
  "yearsOfService": 3
}

### Weekly Report for Employee
GET {{TimeEntryLegacyAPI_HostAddress}}/api/timeentry/report/weekly/1?startDate=2024-11-25
Accept: application/json

